{"tid":538520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"打電話比人，但係聽個個人係我完全唔識？","createTime":"2018-01-23T16:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T16:38:14.000Z","uid":139135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"36709fa747cd0a9c8c6e9644c26f9a5035d75dcf","tid":538520,"uid":139135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"話說呢件事係發生係我小學既時候，其實都唔止發生一次，個時我成日打比一個朋友傾電話，但係聽個個人唔係佢本人都唔係佢啲屋企人，背後仲有啲bb喊聲，而且個個係屋企電話黎，所以我都幾肯定唔會比啲唔識既人聽左。<br />\n有一次我再打過去個時都係同一個狀態，跟住我即刻收左線，再禁多次重撥，點知係我個朋友聽左，我問佢岩岩係唔係有個女人聽左你屋企電話，同埋佢係咪有抱住bb，但係佢話冇，岩岩冇人打過黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e43fd2302aa7b249bba10a9fcb7db9983ce6cb4","tid":538520,"uid":156422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0dee74f70721e0146ae51e40230176dd7c170ad","tid":538520,"uid":156422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:32:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a245b6e33bbff391c242ef262784349b396615e0","tid":538520,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce2ea0d5b7c4c048f1bbe2c34595a7d871a60d43","tid":538520,"uid":156422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:34:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e502691f92ff3a5d22231c58a32c34fe3baf6b6c","tid":538520,"uid":139135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce2ea0d5b7c4c048f1bbe2c34595a7d871a60d43","tid":538520,"uid":156422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a245b6e33bbff391c242ef262784349b396615e0","tid":538520,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:34:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:38:14.000Z","msg":"因為係個一排連續試過幾次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗番起 好奇都正常姐"}]}